{"id":273779,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/奇闻录-盛世一景-1-9/","date":"2013-01-09T17:15:26Z","modified":"2013-01-09T17:15:26Z","title":"奇闻录 | 盛世一景 1-9","content":"<p><p>1月7日，江苏如皋边检站官兵指导驻地长新小学师生与手持菜刀的“歹徒”进行周旋，成功将歹徒“制服”。当日，江苏如皋边检站官兵与驻地长新小学700多名师生共同举行了防暴演习。演习模拟了一名歹徒闯入校园，持刀欲进入教室行凶，学生老师堵住教室前后大门，他们用椅子、扫把与手持菜刀的“歹徒”进行周旋，成功将歹徒“制服”。<span></span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/9512.html/77891986gw1e0n3o3izrij\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/77891986gw1e0n3o3izrij.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=V4mlwQ5xCXc:tmjoNqowmmM:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/qi-wen-lu/~4/V4mlwQ5xCXc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" valu